query:
SELECT lojaId, lojaNome, taxaReparacao, qtdReparacoes, qtdParaBrisas, totalServicos 
FROM resultados_mensais 
WHERE mes = 1 AND ano = 2026 
AND taxaReparacao IS NOT NULL 
LIMIT 10;
